"{\"uid\": \"usmagazine.com-entertainment-news-tom-cruise-was-paid-nothing-for-2024-paris-olympics-stunt\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tom Cruise's payday forperforming a death-defying stuntat the2024 Paris Olympicsclosing ceremony may have been his lowest yet, as the superstar wasn't paid anything at all.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheMission: Impossibleactor's stunt saw him jump from the top of the Stade de France into the stadium where he was handed the Olympic flag by decorated gymnastSimone Bilesand Los Angeles mayorKaren Bass.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 349, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999575781124601, \"rank\": 4.24236608385856e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9796341133083126, \"rank\": 0.020789122647290756, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After retrieving the flag, Cruise jumped on his motorcycle and a pretaped segment showed the actor riding through Paris, boarding a cargo plane to L.A. and arriving at the iconic Hollywood sign.Cruise's jaw-dropping stuntwas the perfect handover to the2028 Los Angeles Olympics.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999964854851, \"rank\": 3.5144229013973505e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9998526585835338, \"rank\": 0.00014736310815126962, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999988694981, \"rank\": 9.713760941801127e-10, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During a \\\"CNBC x Boardroom: Game Plan\\\" panel in Santa Monica on Tuesday, September 10, LA28 president and chairpersonCasey Wassermanshared Cruise's very reasonable fee for performing in Paris.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999986134753, \"rank\": 1.377817324855264e-09, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\", \"score\": 0.9997365349455443, \"rank\": 0.0002635344165512455, \"text\": \"Santa Monica\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Monica_Boulevard\"}, {\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999964854851, \"rank\": 3.5144229013973505e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Confirming that Cruise and his entire team did not take a cent for the impressive performance, Wasserman also explained how the stunt came together in the first place.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9195514947692597, \"rank\": 0.08748667466632241, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The best part of the story is we pitched on a Zoom and the original idea was a person in the stadium as a stunt double,\\\" Wasserman said, viaThe Hollywood Reporter.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9195514947692597, \"rank\": 0.08748667466632241, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wasserman and the team assumed the actor would simply participate in a pretaped segment in L.A. and would be too busy to take part in the Olympics closing ceremony, but the Golden Globe winner had other plans.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9195514947692597, \"rank\": 0.08748667466632241, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9998526585835338, \"rank\": 0.00014736310815126962, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"About five minutes into the presentation, [Tom Cruise] goes, 'I am in.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am only doing it if I get to do everything,'\\\" Wasserman explained.\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1522, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9195514947692597, \"rank\": 0.08748667466632241, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Behind-the-scenes, organizers tried to temper their expectations, believing Cruise would be too busy to actually take part, but he quickly proved them all wrong.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have successfully subscribed.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By signing up, I agree to the Terms and Privacy Policy and to receive emails from Us Weekly  Check our latest news in Google News  Check our latest news in Apple News  When it came to filming in Los Angeles, Cruise did not even let his hectic acting schedule get in the way.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Apple News\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_News\"}, {\"begin\": 1937, \"end\": 1948, \"title\": \"http://